### Login (POST - submit credentials)
# Note: Uses 'username' (not 'email') and 'password'
# Success returns: {"success": true, "message": "Login successful", "csrfToken": "..."}
# The csrfToken must be included in X-CSRF-Token header for ALL authenticated requests
# CSRF validation happens automatically in validate block for ALL HTTP methods (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE)
# Failure returns: {"error": "Invalid credentials"} with 401 status
POST {{MainAppUrl}}/api/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=vshpynta@crud.business&password=1234

###

### Secret page (requires authentication + CSRF token)
# CSRF validation happens in validate block for ALL authenticated requests (including GET)
# First login to get CSRF token from response, then include it in X-CSRF-Token header
# Note: CSRF token is required even for GET requests when using SameSite=None cross-domain cookies
# Error responses:
#   - 401 Unauthorized: No session cookie (need to login)
#   - 403 Forbidden: Invalid/missing CSRF token (check X-CSRF-Token header)
GET {{MainAppUrl}}/api/secret
X-CSRF-Token: f3ff20cb-e20b-404f-b734-42916b84dc9e
Cookie: user-session=e6d34411b03deb9ba4734b8d46ae6551%2F87abcaecb352c77bc92c56182c2d1780d2409392f683ea6a1a8711f64f4d05498f9e67fc4d55bf0e87bfcbce43c007d32858eb671f0e1b3c8589dcfcce1a3d83%3Ab73200c31d4f92ccd2f88b2ae321031b582afb178a097b573b9bf77add42bac6
###

